# Absolute API URL — REQUIRED for production builds (Docker ARG on Railway).
# In dev, leave unset: the admin uses same-origin `/_parfumbox-api` (Vite proxy → :3000),
# which keeps HTTPS tunnels (ngrok) free of mixed-content errors and forwards Socket.IO.
# Cross-origin (Railway): set to the public HTTPS URL of the api service.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
